================================================================================
Significant changes relative to upstream Krypton
================================================================================

  - Revived the dead build: dependencies (formerly served from the now-offline
    repo.kryptonmc.org) restored to a local Maven repository; toolchain
    modernized to JDK 21 / Gradle.
  - Implemented a large set of Minecraft 1.19.3 (protocol 761) gameplay
    features, each verified by autonomous protocol-level test bots: survival
    block drops, full inventory interactions, containers (chests / furnaces /
    hoppers / brewing stands), crafting, XP and levels, mob AI with A*
    pathfinding, natural spawning, redstone (wire / repeater / comparator /
    pistons / dispensers), fluid water, crop growth, fishing, TNT, enchanting,
    potions and status effects, the day-night cycle, sleeping, procedural
    structures (houses / wells / villages / watchtowers / ruins), block sounds
    and particles, and world / player / chest / XP persistence.

See CHANGELOG.md for the full, versioned list of changes.

